trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IWindowProvider"></xref>.
These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.WindowPattern>.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.WindowPattern.WindowPatternInformation.CanMaximize*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.WindowPattern>.
To be added.
